00:06:54.770 --> 00:06:58.440
But Mary also used our
conservation technologies

00:06:58.440 --> 00:07:01.880
to uncover some very interesting
forensics about Madison.

00:07:01.880 --> 00:07:04.710
And we're hoping she'll
talk to us about that.

00:07:04.710 --> 00:07:07.300
Mary is a scholar in her own right.

00:07:07.300 --> 00:07:12.990
But I understand that she comes
from a long line of legal scholars.

00:07:12.990 --> 00:07:18.250
So without further ado, I'm just
going to say one or two more things

00:07:18.250 --> 00:07:23.190
