00:07:23.190 --> 00:07:25.610
about the libraries
which collections with--

00:07:25.610 --> 00:07:29.440
of Madison and the 23 other
presidential collections perhaps

00:07:29.440 --> 00:07:31.330
he'll just mention briefly.

00:07:31.330 --> 00:07:36.390
But we're going to have
