00:24:42.780 --> 00:24:48.700
In 1815, Thomas Jefferson wrote
to John Adams about Madison's note

00:24:48.700 --> 00:24:50.890
of the Constitutional Convention.

00:24:50.890 --> 00:24:54.040
And they were then
not yet published.

00:24:54.040 --> 00:24:58.570
And Jefferson remarked, "The
